{"word":"H3411 - יְרֵכָה - yᵉrêkâh - yer-ay-kaw' - Border","slug":"H3411","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יְרֵכָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yᵉrêkâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yer-ay-kaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Border"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05E8;&#x05DB;&#x05D4; - y<sup>e</sup>re&#x0302;ka&#x0302;h</b> - <i>yer-ay-kaw'</i><p/>Feminine of <a href=\"#/H3409\">H3409</a>; properly the <i>flank</i>; but used only figuratively, the <i>rear</i> or <i>recess: - </i>border, coast, part, quarter, side."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3406\">H3406</a>, <a href=\"#/H3409\">H3409</a>, <a href=\"#/H3412\">H3412</a>, <a href=\"#/H3413\">H3413</a>"}]}